# Mechigram — Core

Applies to `core/`. Full role: `ia/roles/domain-engineer.md`.

- No imports of `os`, HTTP, PDF, or `render`
- Word lengths and indexing use `[]rune(word)`, not byte indices
- `PlaceWord` returns receipt `[]bool`; `RemoveWord` only clears cells where receipt is true
- Min slot length is 4 (parser rule — do not lower without ROADMAP change)
- Solver: inject `*rand.Rand` for shuffle; no global rand in tests

Tests: table-driven, see `ia/standards/testing.md` and `ia/playbooks/write-core-tests/PLAYBOOK.md`.
